<section>
	<h2>Options de configuration des styles</h2>
	<dl class="dl-horizontal">
		<dt><code>form-label-inline</code></dt>
		<dd>Composante: Style incorporé. Utiliser sur chaque étiquette.</dd>
		<dt><code>checkbox-green</code></dt>
		<dd>Composante: Success checkboxes with green background. Apply to each checkbox list item.</dd>
		<dt><code>disabled</code></dt>
		<dd>Composante: Disabled state on form controls. Add ".disabled" to the input field and ".is-disabled" to the checkbox or radio button list item.</dd>
	</dl>
